Dispatch on the contract side is pretty simple:

- For deploy just take all the parameters (arguments) in the order they are listed in the JSON and decode them using SCALE.
- For call the first 4 bytes are encoding the message selector and the rest is again just the SCALE encoded arguments for the selected message.

